# Creating a Microsoft Azure Pass Subscription

## Creating an Azure Pass subscription is a two step process.

1.Redeem your Azure Pass Promo Code  
1.Activate your subscription

## Step 1: Redeeming a Microsoft Azure Pass Promo Code:

Open a browser and navigate to: +++www.microsoftazurepass.com+++

> [!KNOWLEDGE] It is recommended you close all browsers and open a new In-Private Browser session. Other log-ins can persist and cause errors during the activation step.

Click the start button to get started.
	
^IMAGE[Screenshot](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/1.jpg)	

Enter your account login information and select “Sign In”.

^IMAGE[Screenshot](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/2.jpg)
	
Click “Confirm” if the correct email address is listed.

^IMAGE[Screenshot](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/3.jpg)
	
Enter your promo code (available from the **Resources** tab above) in the Promo code box and click “Claim Promo Code”.

^IMAGE[Screenshot](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/4.jpg)
	
It may take up to 5 minutes to process the redemption.

^IMAGE[Screenshot](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/5.jpg)

Click on “Activate” to start setting up your Azure subscription.

^IMAGE[Screenshot](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/6.jpg)
	
## Step 2: Activate your subscription:

Enter your account information and click “Next”.

^IMAGE[Screenshot](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/7.jpg)
	
Enter your phone number and click “Next”.

^IMAGE[Screenshot](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/8.jpg)
	
It may take a few minutes to process the request.

^IMAGE[Screenshot](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/9.jpg)
^IMAGE[Screenshot](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/10.jpg)
^IMAGE[Screenshot](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/11.jpg)
	
Your subscription is ready, click “Get started” to use Azure services.
	
^IMAGE[Screenshot](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/12.jpg)
